DejaVuSans.ttf is part of the DejaVu fonts project and is bundled here to render
QR-code captions with full Latin (accented) coverage.

The DejaVu fonts are based on the Bitstream Vera Fonts and are released under a
free license that permits redistribution. Full license text:
https://dejavu-fonts.github.io/License.html

